We may process Your Sensitive Personal Data where We have, in accordance with applicable law, obtained Your prior, express consent prior to processing Your Sensitive Personal Data (this legal basis is only used in relation to processing that is entirely voluntary - it is not used for processing that is necessary or obligatory in any way).
We may process Your Sensitive Personal Data where the processing is necessary for the detection or prevention of crime (e.g., the prevention of fraud);
We may process Your Sensitive Personal Data where the processing is necessary for the establishment, exercise or defense of legal rights; or
We may process Your Sensitive Personal Data where the processing is required or permitted by applicable law (e.g., to comply with Our diversity reporting obligations);
